00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,720
You don't even admit your mistake.

359
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:32,520
Servants.

360
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:32,960
Yes.

361
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,880
Take him to the ancestral hall

362
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:34,880
