391
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:19,000
It's understandable

392
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,720
that he cares about his birth mother.

393
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,200
Young Madam,

394
00:17:22,310 --> 00:17:24,310
