472
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:20,480
I don't believe

473
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:21,880
that I can't survive

474
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,080
without you and Shiyi.

475
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:25,760
Young Madam.

